title: For Sale:  Hk P7 Grade A
postcontent: I've owned this P7 for about 8 years, it's in great shape and never failed me in any way. It is one of the finest combat handguns ever made with a superb single action trigger. The magazine release is a heel release. I actually prefer this for CCW since there is no concern of the mag release button being hit and releasing the mag. Comes with 2 mags and custom leather holster. The P7 is one of the fastest weapons to reload due to the fact that the grip safety also releases the slide and cocks the weapon making it ready to fire. The fixed polygonal rifled barrel lends to it's accuracy. Some say the most accurate 9mm made. The gas system allows for less recoil as well as assisting with the ejecting of brass due to ports in the chamber area. The gas system also retards recoil for a fraction of a second so that the movement of recoil does not start until after the round has left the barrel. The weapon will eject brass even if the extractor is damaged. The gas system also prevents limp wrist issues. One of the finest weapons ever! I will always keep one in the collection (also have a P7m13).  The weapons is in my name so the purchaser must be legal to own and willing to complete a transfer form. $1,200 firm.  Buyer must meet me in the Enumclaw area. Thanks
